title: American Horror Story (Season 01: Murder House) - Trailer
author: The Film Archives
comment: Murder house is by far the best season.
I don't care what everybody says. In my opinion Murder House is the absolute best season of AHS.

I loved Murder House, although this trailer makes it look like mediocre garbage. It's like it was made by someone with zero talent in neither video nor sound editing who saw one trailer and went "yeah I can do that".
Ok the trailer kinda sucks but the show is really good
